cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this code or methodology, please cite as below."
type: software
title: "BERTopic Media Topics: Embedding-Based Topic Modeling for Media and Communication Research"
abstract: >
  A BERTopic pipeline for thematic analysis of media corpora. Covers sentence
  embeddings, UMAP dimensionality reduction, HDBSCAN clustering, c-TF-IDF topic
  representations, and optional LLM-based semantic labelling. Outputs are exported
  to R for post-hoc engagement analysis. Developed by Sawood Anwar as part of
  doctoral research at the University of Urbino Carlo Bo, Italy (2025).
